Hi everyone .... We played this course earlier in the the year and it was a really pretty course reasonably priced. Green fees are $66 which includes cart. I've booked 3 T times for this Saturday at 11:15am. Weather for this Saturday looks pretty good - high 60's with sun.

$1 will be collected for the website.

Hope to see you there, Cindi 339-224-1377.
